{"tid":1154534,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"溫子仁監製《Mortal Kombat 真人快打》真人化電影澳洲拍攝始動","createTime":"2019-05-14T11:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T15:12:13.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"647c5d7006ed78b14eb9f2c5366f0189701ced9f","tid":1154534,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"出名戰鬥場面極度殘忍嘅格鬥遊戲系列《Mortal Kombat 11（真人快打 11）》已經推出市面，雖然呢隻遊戲喺香港唔算爆多 Fans，但係喺國外就極度受歡迎，外國仲有好多高手臥虎藏龍添！<br />\n<br />\n《MK》雖然係格鬥遊戲，不過亦有好重故事性，所以早於 1995 及 1997 年已經有改篇為真人電影版本。電影我無緣觀看，唔知有無讀者睇過可以品評一下呢？因為遊戲改篇真人電影作品（仲要 90 年代咁古早）真係令人好奇當時係成點&hellip;&hellip;我地一齊黎睇下劇照先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vjgamer.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/14/54737/mortal-kombat-annihilation.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjgamer.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F54737%2Fmortal-kombat-annihilation.jpg&h=36e5cbba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華納兄弟早在 2010 年時就宣佈「會重新拍攝《Mortal Kombat》」，今次仲搵黎恐怖片大導演溫子仁（James Wan）做電影監製，聽落似乎又幾有睇頭！電影目前定名為《Mortal Kombat: Rebirth》，近期就會正式開始進行拍攝工作，主要拍攝將會喺南澳阿得萊德（Adelaide）進行。"},{"pid":"0364e9673b5b9b32ca847782e0ac884ba1c33948","tid":1154534,"uid":236794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"佢拍返鬼片好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab671ed630d42a1e00b8643da02d42a42b9acdf2","tid":1154534,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0364e9673b5b9b32ca847782e0ac884ba1c33948","tid":1154534,"uid":236794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"佢拍返鬼片好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"Conjuring 3 please"},{"pid":"a0cf39509925115e6948dd31f7a8f1155be70778","tid":1154534,"uid":3668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"Flawless victory <img sr